{"tid":1307070,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂已向美國聯邦通信委員會提交了申請，將對舊版Switch的CPU和主機板等進行升級","createTime":"2019-07-11T11:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T15:39:17.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ce25e63a579a992eb3c23bbc70eb1bbd5975d7","tid":1307070,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2377246135879227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2377246135879227&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=0918f188\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2377246135879227</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>#舊版Switch也獲硬件升級CPU及 Ram 主板全面更新換代</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n持續數個月關於任天堂將推出兩個型號新版Switch遊戲機的傳言在昨天夜間被任天堂官方打破，任天堂正式發布了面向傳統掌機用戶的新版Switch Lite。這個新型號不但不能拆卸手柄，而且還不能連接底座和顯示設備輸出遊戲畫面。那麼，喜歡在大屏幕上玩遊戲的Switch潛在用戶就沒有新的選擇了嗎？除了傳言中性能更強的Switch Pro之外，其實，<strong><ins>Nintendo很快將對現有舊版Switch進行&ldquo;更新換代&rdquo;。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n日前，任天堂已經向美國聯邦通信委員會(Federal Communications Commission)提交了修改現有Switch的II類許可申請。根據該文件顯示<strong><ins>，Nintendo將更換當前型號Switch的SoC、NAND  Ram和主板。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，任天堂為 Switch 採用了來自 Nvidia Tegra X1芯片，該芯片使用 20nm 工藝，是2015年產品的定製版，在初期推出的兩千萬台Switch還因為芯片內的漏洞導致被輕易破解。所以，<strong><ins>Nintendo 很可能會通過這一次的改動，為舊版 Switch 搭配相對更加省電並且打好安全補丁的新版SoC</ins></strong>。另外，隨著手機行業更多地使用64GB Ram作為標配，Nintendo 採購Switch 內置的32GB Ram也許並不能獲得足量供貨，因此<strong><ins>這次硬件改動也有望將Ram容量升級至64GB</ins></strong>，畢竟現在玩家更傾向於購買數字版，而且遊戲的容量也愈來愈大。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，<strong><ins>本次申請並沒有涉及Soc及NAND之外的內容，也就是說Switch玩家詬病已久的Joy-Con搖桿&ldquo;漂移&rdquo;等問題也許仍然將原味保留。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>[老任新機已出] Switch游戲太少? 任天堂最新發布的Switch宣傳片高調進行反駁!</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1303785/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1303785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[任天堂就是道路、真理、生命] 任天堂正考慮在中國以外的國家建立新的主機製造廠</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1301855/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1301855/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>任天堂正式發表「Nintendo Switch Lite」 9月發售, , 約$1500</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1303755/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1303755/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6ca99df89aa6e0a14d117a89abfb546021aee559","tid":1307070,"uid":64454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"Ram定Rom呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518a77eccc83a4cc55bd13c92faef3695a4c404d","tid":1307070,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"6ca99df89aa6e0a14d117a89abfb546021aee559","tid":1307070,"uid":64454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"Ram定Rom呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"應該係ram啦，rom係系統"},{"pid":"0c6dad6eb34c471ba9159e27dc3c178810682372","tid":1307070,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"RAM on9"},{"pid":"c068f68e4746c73fe84c58bfad6dfc56bea5553f","tid":1307070,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"6ca99df89aa6e0a14d117a89abfb546021aee559","tid":1307070,"uid":64454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"Ram定Rom呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"原文寫&quot;內存&quot;，我改晒做RAM <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f869ba0724b13595074c805d0aa5fa891e1860ea","tid":1307070,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8fd7dd361465a0ab19ddb54546694a5eadf278","tid":1307070,